From: Sam Thursfield <sam.thursfield@codethink.co.uk>
Date: Tue, 5 May 2026 12:55:56 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 09/16] FDSDK 26.08: Use hidapi from FDSDK

This wasn't available in FDSDK 25.08, but it will be around in the
upcoming 26.08 release.
---
 elements/sdk/hidapi.bst         | 18 ------------------
 elements/sdk/libmanette-0.2.bst |  2 +-
 elements/sdk/libmanette.bst     |  2 +-
 3 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 20 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 elements/sdk/hidapi.bst

diff --git a/elements/sdk/hidapi.bst b/elements/sdk/hidapi.bst
deleted file mode 100644
index 1938a1593..000000000
--- a/elements/sdk/hidapi.bst
+++ /dev/null
@@ -1,18 +0,0 @@
-kind: cmake
-
-sources:
-- kind: tar
-  url: github_files:libusb/hidapi/archive/refs/tags/hidapi-0.14.0.tar.gz
-  ref: a5714234abe6e1f53647dd8cba7d69f65f71c558b7896ed218864ffcf405bcbd
-
-build-depends:
-- freedesktop-sdk.bst:public-stacks/buildsystem-cmake.bst
-
-depends:
-- freedesktop-sdk.bst:public-stacks/runtime-minimal.bst
-- freedesktop-sdk.bst:components/systemd-libs.bst
-
-variables:
-  cmake-local: >-
-    -DHIDAPI_WITH_LIBUSB=OFF
-    -DCMAKE_POLICY_VERSION_MINIMUM=3.5
diff --git a/elements/sdk/libmanette-0.2.bst b/elements/sdk/libmanette-0.2.bst
index dbd63cf24..4e7845526 100644
--- a/elements/sdk/libmanette-0.2.bst
+++ b/elements/sdk/libmanette-0.2.bst
@@ -13,7 +13,7 @@ build-depends:
 
